SUMMARY:Unionize for Trans Rights - Campaign Kickoff
DESCRIPTION:Interested in exploring what a labor-focused approach to winning trans rights might look like? Come help brainstorm and sketch out the early phases of our Unionize for Trans Rights​ campaign! \nWe’ll be at Big Time Brewery​ in the U District for a working-social where we’ll discuss how we can help trans and nonbinary workers organize their workplaces and enshrine protections into union contracts. This is also an opportunity for those looking to get involved with this campaign to get to know one another—we hope you’ll join us! \nRSVP here!
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/unionize-for-trans-rights-campaign-kickoff/
LOCATION:WA
CATEGORIES:New Member Friendly,Socials,Trans Rights and Bodily Autonomy Working Group
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://seattledsa.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/signal-2026-03-26-115057.jpeg
END:VEVENT
