SUMMARY:Immigration Justice Working Group Migrant Accompaniment Training
DESCRIPTION:ICE is kidnapping our neighbors off the streets and at their immigration and legal appointments. Join us to be trained in accompanying migrants to their appointments\, to help protect their legal rights\, and connect them to critical resources. \nAll volunteers providing accompaniment must be willing to opt into a state background check.
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/immigration-justice-working-group-migrant-accompaniment-training-2/
LOCATION:WA
END:VEVENT
