SUMMARY:Hiking Club to Teneriffe Falls 🌹
DESCRIPTION:We’re socialists who hike! \nApril we’ll be hiking Teneriffe Falls (5.6 miles) in the North Bend area. Let’s enjoy some early season hiking. DSA membership not required. \nMeet in the Hilltop Red Apple parking lot. Snacks and transportation to the trail provided.
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/hiking-club-to-teneriffe-falls/
LOCATION:WA
CATEGORIES:Arts & Culture
