SUMMARY:Pride Month Planning Meeting
DESCRIPTION:Seattle DSA is gearing up for Pride Month 2026! Comrades from several working groups and committees have come together to prepare for tabling at events like Trans Pride Seattle and to host our own DSA Pride Event. If you’d like to get involved in these efforts please join us for our biweekly planning sessions! \nThis is an internal event for DSA members. Meeting info can be found on Discord and in our Signal chat.
