CREATED:20260401T170012Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260401T171403Z
UID:10018334-1775408400-1775413800@seattledsa.org
SUMMARY:Socialist analysis: War in Iran - Where is this heading and how do we fight it?
DESCRIPTION:War in Iran\nWhere is this heading and how do we fight it?\nThis Sunday\, April 5\n5pm\nVictrola Cafe (411 15th Ave E) Community room\n  \nThe war rages unabated.  Where is this heading? Will there be a ground invasion? Nuclear weapons? What does the war tell us about US and Israeli imperialism? How can the socialist movement\, the labor movement\, and the Left build a fighting anti-war movement? \nWe’ll also discuss the tension between Mayor Wilson and the Left on surveillance and the NYC-DSA AOC endorsement debate. \nEveryone is welcome – you do not need to live in D3 to attend!
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/socialist-analysis-war-in-iran-where-is-this-heading-and-how-do-we-fight-it/
LOCATION:Victrola Coffee (411 15th Ave E)\, 411 15th Ave E\, Seattle\, WA\, 98112\, United States
CATEGORIES:New Member Friendly
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://seattledsa.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/download-1.jpg
GEO:47.6223738;-122.312808
