DESCRIPTION:This is the biweekly sync-up for Seattle DSA’s Trans Rights and Bodily Autonomy (TRBA) group\, as we plan actions to defend and advocate for trans\, queer\, and women’s liberation in Seattle and the Pacific Northwest. \nWe are currently holding virtual calls through Signal. The Signal group chat link for the meeting is provided via email after RSVP’ing. \n 
