SUMMARY:North End Ecosocialism Reading Group
DESCRIPTION:Join us at Armistice Coffee Roosevelt\, to discuss the book Practical Radicals: Seven Strategies to Change the World\, by Deepak Bhargava and Stephanie Luce\, through the end of Chapter 14. \nYou don’t have to live in the north end\, and you can feel free to join the conversation even if you haven’t had time to read.  Our biweekly discussions seek to inform strategies for winning a democratic socialist society that thrives ecologically. All are welcome! \nWe sit outdoors in a breezeway–dress warm. Any questions or difficulty getting the book\, please email greennewdeal@seattledsa.org.
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/north-end-ecosocialism-reading-group-5/
LOCATION:Armistice Coffee Roosevelt\, 6717 Roosevelt Ave NE\, Seattle\, WA
CATEGORIES:Ecosocialism,Green New Deal,New Member Friendly,Reading Groups
END:VEVENT
