SUMMARY:Socialist Educators Happy Hour
DESCRIPTION:Socialist Educators Happy Hour\nEducators from all over (Seattle\, Renton\, Highline\, etc…) get together\, chat politics\, & share about struggles in their union. All union activists and socialists are welcome to attend! \nWe often anchor our discussions with a reading\, but we’ll provide a short summary so everyone can participate whether they read or not. \nWe meet 6pm every 2nd Friday of the month at Chuck’s Hop Shop in the Central District. Join us!
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/socialist-educators-happy-hour-12/2026-05-08/
LOCATION:Chuck’s Hop Shop (Central District)\, 2001 E Union St\, Seattle\, WA\, 98122\, United States
